            <title>OpenStack dashboard — Admin tab</title>
            <paragraph>Administrative users can use the <inline classes="guilabel" rawtext=":guilabel:`Admin`">Admin</inline> tab to view usage and to
                manage instances, volumes, flavors, images, networks, and so on.</paragraph>
