                            through VNC.</paragraph>
                    </list_item>
                    <list_item>
                        <paragraph><inline classes="guilabel" rawtext=":guilabel:`Volumes`">Volumes</inline>: Use the following tabs to complete these tasks:</paragraph>
                        <bullet_list bullet="*">
                            <list_item>
                                <paragraph><inline classes="guilabel" rawtext=":guilabel:`Volumes`">Volumes</inline>: View, create, manage, and delete volumes.</paragraph>
                            </list_item>
                            <list_item>
                                <paragraph><inline classes="guilabel" rawtext=":guilabel:`Volume Types`">Volume Types</inline>: View, create, manage, and delete volume types.</paragraph>
                            </list_item>
                            <list_item>
                                <paragraph><inline classes="guilabel" rawtext=":guilabel:`Volume Snapshots`">Volume Snapshots</inline>: View, manage, and delete volume snapshots.</paragraph>
                            </list_item>
